These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, september, april, july, october, february, january
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, gardening, skydiving, magic-tricks, reading, fishing, dancing
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Birthday   | july | november | january | september    | april | october   | february    |
| Hobby         | fishing  | gardening   | magic-tricks | baking | skydiving   | dancing | reading |

