.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, tennis, rowing, sailing, skateboarding, surfing, cycling
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, horror, martial-arts, romance, documentary, epic
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person watching documentary movies##2
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Sport          | skateboarding | rowing | surfing | tennis | cycling | rugby      | sailing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | martial-arts  | epic     | horror     | romance  | scientific | animation |

