.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, sprite, tea, hot-chocolate, milk, lemonade
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, old-henry, aristoff, baccarat, cain, swisher, prince
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 3. the cain-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking tea is the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the person drinking tea##2
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate | 7up | mirinda   | tea | sprite | milk |
| Cigar           | cain | swisher     | old-henry     | aristoff | baccarat   | alhambra   | prince    |

