.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
House: cape-cod, colonial, farmhouse, gothic-revival, craftsman, victorian, art-deco
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, rock, trance, soul, ambient, dubstep, r&b
 1. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan trance##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the fan ambient##1
 3. the fan dubstep is on the right of the fan soul##1
 4. the craftsman house is on the right of the fan ambient##1
 5. the fan folk is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the fan soul is between the farmhouse house and the fan dubstep##2
 7. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
 8. the fan soul is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the colonial house is the fan rock##1
10. the fan folk is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| House      | farmhouse    | craftsman  | gothic-revival  | cape-cod  | art-deco      | victorian       | colonial |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | soul | dubstep | r&b | folk | trance | rock  |

