.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, mouse, pony, fish, dog, snake
There are 7 different favourite colors: ebony, azure, coral, amber, black, blue, brown
1. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes black is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person who likes ebony is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the hamster##2
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who likes black##1
5. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes blue is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes black##1
8. the person who likes azure is the owner of the pony##1
9. the owner of the fish is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Pet   | pony      | fish | hamster | mouse | snake      | chinchilla      | dog |
| Color     | azure | blue | brown       | ebony | coral | black | amber |

