.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, airplane, quad-bike, van, taxi, tram
7 different pets are kept: pony, bird, rabbit, frog, chinchilla, rat, goldfish
 1. the owner of the rat is the person driving the van##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the goldfish##2
 5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the frog is the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person driving the van##2
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Transport   | roller | motorbike    | quad-bike | airplane   | taxi | tram    | van |
| Pet      | frog | pony | goldfish    | bird | chinchilla    | rabbit | rat  |

