.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There 7 different types of food: plum, cherry, banana, pumpkin, avocado, orange, artichoke
7 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, snake, hamster, dog, guinea-pig, mouse
 1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 6. the person eating orange is between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating artichoke##2
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the person eating cherry is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating plum##2
11. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Food   | banana  | avocado   | plum         | cherry     | artichoke              | orange    | pumpkin     |
| Pet        | guinea-pig | rabbit | dog | hamster | mouse | fish | snake |

