.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, airplane, train, boat, helicopter, car
There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, blood-red, light-blue, apricot, ebony, ivory, yellow
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person driving the train is between the person who likes ebony and the person driving the taxi##2
7. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the car##2
8. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Transport   | car | helicopter       | airplane    | boat | train | taxi     | quad-bike       |
| Color   | blood-red    | apricot | ivory | ebony        | light-blue | turquise | yellow |

