 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking water##2
 5. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating potato##1
