 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the japanese##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the indonesian##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the spanish##1
10. the spanish is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
