.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-20::.
7 different games are played: chess, scrabble, monopoly, domino, canasta, bridge, billiard
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, april, june, march, january, february, september
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing domino and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person playing chess##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person playing billiard and the person who's birthday is in february##2
9. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
| Game   | bridge | scrabble    | chess | billiard | domino              | monopoly      | canasta    |
| Birthday    | april | june | march  | january   | september | february | november |

 